ss="_ _6"></span>如果你</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y70 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">学佛，人人都会蔑视你，上上下下把你当“怪物”一样看；</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y45 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">而学佛的人，<span class="_ _d"></span>自己也胆战心惊，<span class="_ _d"></span>慢慢地，<span class="_ _d"></span>也觉得自己挺怪的。<span class="_ _7"></span> </div><div class="t m0 xc h4 y72 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">我认为直率一点好，<span class="_ _c"></span><span class="ls2f">尤其是佛教徒，<span class="_ _18"></span>信佛就说自己信佛。</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y73 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">但我遇到一个领导，<span class="_ _c"></span><span class="ls2b">明明已经皈依很长时间了，<span class="_ _18"></span><span class="ls16">家里有佛堂，</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y74 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">也一直在念佛，但我问他：<span class="_ _7"></span>“你是不是佛教徒？”<span class="_ _7"></span>“不不不，</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y75 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">我不是！<span class="_ _6"></span>我只是研究佛教，<span class="_ _a"></span>喜欢看看，<span class="_ _6"></span>但我不信，<span class="_ _a"></span>我们不信</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y7d ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">仰这个……”其实这大可不必。 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
